====================
OpenERP e-learning
====================

Source code e-learning App for Django. Show Training OpenERP (course, offers, subscriptions, exams,...) in your webpage.

Requeriments
============

#. Training Modules OpenERP
    - training_exam
    - training_django
    - training_exam_django

    https://code.launchpad.net/openerp-training
    
#. Django 1.3

#. OOOP. OpenObject On Python 
    You can download OOOP github project:
    https://github.com/zikzakmedia/ooop

Configuration
=============

#. Edit config.py with OpenERP connection. If you have install Pyro Protocol, you can use this protocol. Default Protocol is XML-RPC

#. Install OpenERP Modules availables addons-extra:
    * training
    * training_elearning
    * training_exam
    * training_doc
    * training_django

